{"tid":698803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[政府派$4000+綜援三糧]綜援生果金週五「出三糧」","createTime":"2018-06-12T04:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T11:13:51.000Z","uid":103207,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"18212e98f216bdaa4b82f68795ef8e593a0afc56","tid":698803,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:37:14.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府星期五向領取綜援、高齡津貼長者生活津貼等人發放額外兩個月金額。<br />\n<br />\n現時<span style=\"color: red;\">領取俗稱「生果金」高齡津貼的長者，可額外獲發兩個月金額，合共2690元。</span><br />\n<br />\n由於<span style=\"color: red;\">早前政府宣佈派發4000元，社署會向長者補發1310元差額，而長者生活津貼可額外獲發6970元，普通傷殘津貼及綜援同樣會出三糧，金額不足4000元，社署會補回差額</span>，相關人士毋須提出申請。<br />\n<br />\n社署已獲撥款約74億元落實有關安排，週五以自動轉帳方式存入領款人的銀行戶口。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辛辛苦苦出黎做十幾年野都冇出過三糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18495938eebec451ba229857bb9291fa0205a34c","tid":698803,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:38:17.000Z","msg":"辛辛苦苦做完拎去補貼俾班垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1a61db40207c63b0ca273eaf17481c66b107fd","tid":698803,"uid":86841,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:39:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b891b809f58ac18168ed6d7b196d91a6b7a523a","tid":698803,"uid":46943,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:46:57.000Z","msg":"支持出三糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大前提係佢地唔可以投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ccaf569aed078d77b97879c8edf8db22b610096","tid":698803,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b891b809f58ac18168ed6d7b196d91a6b7a523a","tid":698803,"uid":46943,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:46:57.000Z","msg":"支持出三糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大前提係佢地唔可以投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime"